DarkMouse::

She went over and got a few cubes of energon and sat down at a table. 
She crossed her legs and nibbled at a cube. "So, please tell me of 
what changes have happened while I slept. You mentioned that you and 
Magnus were close. Tell me, what became of him. For some strange 
reason, "she took a bite and swallowed,"I kind of miss the bot. But 
then, I miss so many lately." She sighed and looked at the partially 
eaten cube in her hand. She suddenly didn't feel hungry. She felt 
loss. She missed KitKat and StarScream. She missed GoldenEye and that 
spider she hung out with. She missed Quickstrike and Arachnia. She 
missed then all and wondered what became of the. Perhaps, one day, 
she'd find out.
She looked up at Galvatron. "Eh, uh, don't mind me. Just rememering 
things from a log time ago." she put the energon back on the tray and 
just sat there, staring into the past.
